description:
The bracelet comes in the following colors:

•Oranges- yellow-orange, regular, light

•Yellows- bright, dark, regular

•Greens- dark, lime, light

•Blues- dark, light, indigo 

•Purples- lavender, deep, regular

•Pinks-dark  magenta, magenta, hot pink, regular, light, extra light

•Browns- brown, tan, reddish-brown

•Greys- white, light beige, black

•Tie dyes-white-pink-blue, blue-green-pink-yellow, green-blue-red, purple-blue-green, blue-red-yellow-orange, green-blue-orange-pink, pink-yellow-green, purple-red-yellow

Contact me with a series of 5 colors (they may be fewer than five) when you order.
